Celani Sikhakhane
Kusuka emigwaqeni ewubhuqu e-Alexandra owayeyiMeya yaseGoli uMpho Moerane oshone kuleli sonto wenze konke okusemandleni ukuphila impilo yakhe.
I-Alex yaziwa njengendawo ehlala imindeni eminingi empofu futhi intsha eningi iphendukela ebugebengwini. Kodwa uMoerane osemncane wathatha indlela ehlukile enobuhlakani.
Ngemuva kokuphothula umatikuletsheni wakhe esikoleni sambanga aphezulu e-Minerva waqhubeka nokuthola isitifiketi sobunjiniyela enza ugesi. Ngemuva kwalokho ube esejoyina
... 
i lwabantu basemalokishini okuhlanganisa ne-Alex lwamphusha ukuba alwele amalungelo abo. Uphakamise ukuthi u-Eskom usule isikweletu sabantu base-Alexandra, i-Soweto, i-Phiri, i-Pimville, i-Orange Farm namanye amalokishi nezindawo ezihlala abantu abampofu.
Akwenzekanga, kodwa uMoerane waqhubeka nokulwela abampofu ngesikhathi esebenza ezikhundleni eziningi ze-ANC esifundeni saseGoli, okuhlanganisa nokuba ngumgcinimafa wesifunda.
Ubeyilungu lebhodi le-Chancellor House uphiko lokutshalwa kwezimali l
...
andla ngokubambisana obekuholwa i-DA.
UMoerane ukhonjwe indlela esikhundleni sokuba nguSihlalo we-ANC e-GreaterJohannesburg Region engqungqutheleni yokukhetha ubuholi ehlehliswe ngempelasonto edlule ngenxa yezingxabano emagatsheni.
UMoerane ushone ngoLwesithathu ngenxa yokulimala engozini yemoto.
Ushiye emhlabeni umkakhe uFikile nezingane ezine.
Inkonzo yesikhumbuzo sakhe izoba ngoLwesihlanu enkundleni ebizwa ngeKwabhekilanga e-Alexandra kanti inkonzo yomngcwabo izoba sendaweni efanayo ngeSonto.

o kuyindlela ekahle yokonga isikhathi namandla amaningi, inqobo nje uma ikhalenda lakho namasethingi kubuyekezwa njalo.

Thabani Maphumulo
ABENHLANGANO iSibaya Community banikele ngezinsiza zokuvikela ubhubhane iCovid-19 nokuyizimfonyo.USihlalo walenhlangano ophinde abe usomabhizinisi odumile eThekwini namaphethelo uVivian Reddy wamukelise isheke kuNdunankulu wesifundazwe uSihle Zikalala kanye noNgqongoqshe woMnyango wezeMpilo esifundazweni uNomagugu Simelane-Zulu.
Zilinganiselwa ku-300 000 izimfonyo enikele ngazo lenhlangano nezidle imali elinganiselwa ku-R4,5 million wezigidi zamarandii. UReddy uthe isinqumo sab
... 
ningo luveza ukuthi ukufaka izimfonyo enye yezindlela esebenzayo ukuvimba ukusabalala kwegciwane. Emva kokuzwa ukuthi kunokushoda kwezimfonyo sibone kufanele singenelele. Kuthina akukho okubalulekile okudlula ukuhlenga izimpilo zomphakathi,” kusho Reddy.
Lo somabhizinisi uqinisekise ukuthi lezimfonyo bazozidlulisela kuhulumeni wesifundazwe bese uzidlulisela emphakathini nakulabo abazidingayo njengabahlengikazi, odokotela,isemitholampilo nakulabo abasebenza emphakathini. UReddy uphinde wadlulisa 
...
o ngalesikhathi nabenza umsebenzi omuhle, ngiyathemba lezinsiza esizikhiphayo zizokwazi uiubavikela kulolubhubhane. Okwesibili ngifisa ukukhumbuza umphakathi ukuthi umuntu unomphefumulo owodwa ngakho ke kumele akuhloniphe lokho. Abantu abajwayele ukuqhelelane baphume emakhaya ngoba kunento ebalulekile abayoyithenga.
Lokhu kuza emva kokuba inhlangano iVivian Reddy Foundation isanda kunikela ngamanabukeni nemiswibela engadla imali engu-R700 000 kuhulumeni wesifundazwe ngasekuqaleni kwaleligciwane.

UPule Mmodi ukholelwa ekutheni iKaizer Chiefs ‘ingaligoba’ irekhodi leMamelodi Sundowns lokungahlulwa kwiDStv Premiership uma la maqembu esetholana phezulu eFNB Stadium ngoLwesine ebusuku.
ISundowns kaRulani Mokwena izoqinisekisa ukuthi idla isicoco sesikhombisa seDStv Premiership kulandelana kusasele imidlalo eyisithupha uma ingahlula Amakhosi.
Izoba nasethubeni elihle lokuthi iqophe irekhodi lokuqeda isizini ingazange ishaywe nakanye.
Kuze kube manje, lezi zinkunzi zaseTshwane azikahlulwa emid
... 
phuma ekunoqbeni iSuperSport futhi ngicabanga ukuthi sikhuthazekile ukudlala neSundowns,” kusho uMmodi kuleli sonto.
“Banerekhodi elihle kunawo wonke amaqmebu kwiligi futhi sizimisele ukuwuqeda lowo mlando.
“Ngicabanga ukuthi okuwukuphela kwendlela yokubahlula ukuthi sonke senze okusemandleni ethu ngoLwesine, ukuze sikwazi ukuthola amaphuzu amathathu …
“Sidinga amaphuzu ukuze sihlale kwiTop 8” kwengeza lo mdlali osayine kwiChiefs esuka kwiGolden Arrows ekuqaleni kwesizini.
Njengamanje iChiefs is
...
shaya amagoli,” kwengeza uMmodi.
“Uma singasebenzisa amathuba esiwatholayo emidlalweni…. konke kuzolunga.”
UMmodi uyazi ukuthi naye sekunesikhathi agcina ukubhakuzisa inethi futhi uthi usekulambele.
Wagcina ukuyibhakuzisa ngoZibandlela bebhekene nePolokwane City.
“Sekunesikhathi eside ngingawashayi amagoli kodwa uma ngingalishayi igoli, kungcono ngisize uzakwethu.
“Kube kungikhungathekisa (ukungashayi amagoli) … kodwa ngicabanga ukuthi ngizokulungisa,” kusho lo mdlali oneminyaka engu-31 ubudala.

Kushone 3 engozini yesitimela eNdiya
2012-05-31 14:02
New Delhi - Kushone okungenani abantu abathathu kwathi abanye balimala ngesikhathi ingxenye yesitimela iphuma kujantshi edolobheni elisenyakatho neNdiya, i-Uttar Pradesh ngoLwesine, kusho umbiko wabezindaba.
Lesi sitimela besisuka eHowrah ngaseKolkata siya eDehradun, e-Uttarakhand.
Kutholakale izidumbu ezintathu, kusho amaphoyisa agada kojantshi.
Luyaqhubeka uhlelo lokutakula abantu abavaleleke ngaphakathi esitimeleni.
Imbangela yale ngozi ayikaziwa.

2020
NgoFebhuwari, iVietnam Yongxin Co., Ltd., inkampani engaphansi kweNkampani yaphesheya kwezilwandle, yahlanganiswa eDolobheni laseHo Chi Minh, eVietnam, nenhlokodolobha ebhalisiwe engu-USD 1 million;
NgoJuni, bekuyikhandidethi lebhizinisi elibalulekile le-Jiangsu Internet Economy “Inkulungwane Eyinkulungwane Nezinkulungwane Eziyishumi” Project.
NgoJulayi, iNkampani yakleliswa kuqala enanini eliphelele lokungenisa kanye nelesishiyagalolunye yenani eliphelele lokuthekelisa e-Nanjing engxenyeni yokuqala ka-2020 ngokwezibalo ze-Jinling Customs.

Uma ufuna ukuvakasha okuphelele, ungabheki kude kuno- “The Leaf River Yacht Club”. Le ndlu eyakhiwe ngamapulangwe enhle izokwenza uzizwe usekhaya njengokungathi use-The Smoky Mountains yase-Tennessee. Yakhiwe ngo-2014, leli khaya linikeza ukubukwa okuhlaba umxhwele komfula omude & ojikelezayo weqabunga, i-sandbar engamakhilomitha angu-1, imisindo engenamkhawulo yemvelo nezinyoni ezihlabelelayo, kanye nokuthula nokuthula. Itholakala kumakhilomitha angu-1.8 ukusuka emnyama, le ndawo yokuvakasha ikuvumela ukuba uphinde uxhumane nemvelo futhi uvuselele kabusha ukugaya kwansuku zonke.

By: Zilungile Mkhize
Umkhakha wezokuvakasha kanye nezindawo zokudlela nokungcebeleka kulelizwe, ukholelwa ukuthi okubi sekwenzekile kwadlula manje.
Ochwepheshe kulezimboni zombili banethemba lokuthi isikhathi sobunzima nesifike nezinkinga eziningi lapho bekuvalwe yonke into ethinta lemikhakha sesidlulile manje.
Bathi amalungiselelo aqhubekayo njengamanje ngawokuqinisekisa ukuthi umnotho kulemboni uyasimama futhi kulandela ukungenzi kahle okwadalwa ukuvalwa kwezwe ngaphansi kwezigaba ezahlukene.
Khonamanjalo, oyisikhulu esiphezulu enkampanini ephethe uxhaxha lwama hhotela kuleli u-Anthony Leeming, uthi isimo sesiqalile ukuba ngcono yize bese kuphele izinyanga besebenza ngaphansi kwengcindezi abanye bevale ngci amabhizinisi abo.
Ekhuluma engqungqutheleni iThink Big Series ebanjwe ngezobuchwepheshe, uLeeming ubeka kanje.

LUCKY CAIN
IKHUZA ibuya isibizwa ngegama elisha indawo yobumnandi eyaduma iNingizimu Afrika nakwamanye amazwe, i-Eyadini Lounge, ekwa-V, eMlazi. Le ndawo kulindeleke ukuba ivulwe ngokusemthethweni ngomcimbi wezinsuku ezintathu, kusukela mhla ka-30 kwephezulu nonyaka. Isizobizwa ngeBlack Bottle Liquors.
Ngokusho komnikazi wayo omusha, uMnu Siwaphiwe Mlobeli (osesithombeni), uhlela ukwenza indumezulu yomcimbi ukubuyisa le ndawo ebantwini.
Uthe kulezi zinsuku ezintathu kuzobe kuboshelwe oDJ nabaculi abadumile eThekwini nasezweni lonke jikelele. “Sihlela ukuphothula uhlu lwabazonandisa ngesonto elizayo, kodwa bazobe bekhona abantu abafana noDJ Tira, uDlala Thukzin noDJ Bongz. Abanye sisa-xoxa nabo,” esho.
Uthe akasilona ivukana kwezobumnandi. “Sengisebenze emicimbini eyahlukene, ngisabalalisa iziphuzo njengoba inkampani yami, iBlack Bottle Liquors, yaziwa ngalo msebenzi. Ngakho ukuvula le ndawo, kuzobe kuwukwengeza emsebenzini ebengiwenza,” esho. Uthe akukho okutheni azokushintsha ngaphandle kokukhuphula izinga endaweni ebivele ikhona.
Le ndawo izovulwa zonke izinsuku, kanti uLwesihlanu, uMgqibelo, iSonto, uMsombuluko noLwesithathu kuzobe kuyizinsuku zemicimbi.

Inhlanganiso edinga ukulotshwa kutsha kwesisekelo sombuso, iNational Constituional Assembly ithi ngoLwesibili lweviki ezayo izaba lokutshengisela kokukhuthaza ukubunjwa kohlangothi oluzabusa okwesikhatshana, iTransitional Authority. Lanxa imibiko ephume emaphephandebeni isithi loku kutshengisela kuqoqwe ndawonye lenhlanganiso yezisebenzi, iZCTU, unobhala jikelele walinhlanganiso, uMnu. Wellington Chibhebhe ulandule lokhu esithi bona khona bezahlangana ukuze baqoqe abazakwenza. Umgcinisihlalo wohlangothi lwabasakhulayo ku NCA, uMnu Alois Dzvairo utshele uChris Gande weStudio 7 ukuthi bakhangelele ukuthi ukutshengisela lokhu kuphumelele ngoba uzulu esethwele nzima ngokungavumelani ekwabeni kwezikhundla zedale lecabinet.

"Khonzani omunye nomunye ngokumanga okungcwele. Amasonto kaKristu akubingelela."- AmaRoma 16: 16
Siyakwamukela kuwebhusayithi yethu. Ukuvakashelwa kwakho lapha kuyakwazisa kakhulu, futhi sithandazela ukuthi uzofuna ukusivakashela emuntwini njengoba sikhulekela iNkosi yethu uMninimandla onke njengomndeni owodwa.
Kule website ungafunda kabanzi mayelana namasonto kaKristu. Ungabhalisela izifundo zeBhayibheli, noma ungathintana nathi mayelana nanoma yimiphi imibuzo ongayithola mayelana neBhayibheli.
Isonto likaKristu ngumndeni wabantwana bakaNkulunkulu abasindiswa ngomusa kaNkulunkulu futhi bazibophezele ekukhonzeni iNkosi yethu kanye nabanye abantu. Kunamabandla amaningi emabandleni kaKristu ngokusebenzisa umhlaba wonke. Ebandleni leNkosi uzothola abantu bazo zonke izizukulwane kanye nokuhamba okuningi kokuphila okuye kwabizelwa ekuhlanganyeleni ubunye nothando nokwamukelwa. Siyajabula ngezipho eziyigugu iNkosi asinike yona, futhi sifisa ukuhlanganyela lezi zipho nezibusiso kuwe. Sicela wazi ukuthi kukhona indawo ekhethekile wena nomndeni wakho phakathi kwamasonto kaKristu.

uthi umufi ubekusho kugcwale umlomo ukuthi umnakwabo akamfihleli ukuthi akamfuni, okwenze (umufi) wagcina esemthatha njengesitha sakhe.

“Unina ka-sbari ubeyithanda le ntombazane ngoba inemali, yize indodana yakhe ibizifela ngodadewethu.

THANDI ZONDI
UKHUZA ibuya kumabonakude uLeleti Khumalo (osesithombeni) ongumlingisi owazakhela udumo elingisa emdlalweni onohlonze, iSarafina. Lo makadebona womlingisi uzobonakala kuMuvhango otshengiswa kuSABC 2, osuzoshaya ngonyawo olusha ngemuva kokuhlaba ikhefu lesikhashana.
Lo mdlalo osuqede iminyaka ewu-27, uqhamuka nonyawo olusha kepha uzoqhubeka nokuhlonipha ulimi lweTshivenda nosiko lwalesi sizwe. Kuzoshintsha i-logo, ibika, kufakwe abalingisi abasha nengqikithi yomdlalo entsha. ULeleti uzolingisa indawo kaDkt Nonhlanhla Ximba osemkhakheni wezokwakha, ozobanga ukushisa kulo mdlalo. Kulesi sigaba esisha soMuvhango, ababhali bathembisa okuzokwenza ababukeli bahlale banganyakazi lapho bebuka umabonakude.
UDuma Ndlovu ongumbhali woMuvhango, uthe: “UMuvhango akusona isiqalo esisha kuphela, kepha sigubha nefa lomdlalo. Sizinikele ngokubambelela ezimpandeni zethu, samukela noshintsho. Sijabule ngokulethela ababukeli uMuvhango ozoveza ukwehlukana kwabantu baseNingizimu Afrika yesimanje,” esho.
Oyibamba lenhloko yesiteshi sakwaSABC 2, uJacqui Hlongwane, uthe bazimisele ngokweseka uMuvhango kuleli khasi elisha. “Selokhu kwathi nhlo, lo mdlalo uyinsika yezinhlelo zethu, sikulindele ngentokozo okusha oza nakho kubabukeli bethu,” esho.

NgeSonto ekuseni, kubikwe ukuthi indawo ye-National Sea Rescue Institute’s Station 16 e-Strandfontein igqekeziwe. Ngosuku olulodwa ntambama, kutholakele izinsalela zesikebhe sokuhlenga esintshontshiwe.
Okhulumela amaphoyisa ase-Western Cape, uLieutenant Colonel Malcolm Pojie uthe ingidi yegalaji elise-Station 16 ibigqekeziwe ngaphambi kokuthi izigebengu zingene bese ziphuma nesikebhe sokuhlenga esisetshenziswa ezimeni eziphuthumayo olwandle ngabasebenzi bakwa-Strandfontein.
Isexwayiso sisakazwe ngokushesha ihhovisi elikhulu le-NSRI eKapa, ukuze abantu olwandle babheke i-JetRIB ebomvu (isikebhe esiqinile esi-inflatable) esibhalwe ngokucacile ukuthi “NSRI Rescue 16A”.
Okhulumela i-NSRI uthe lesi sigameko ngesokuqala yize izimpahla eziphathwayo ezifana ne-Pink Rescue Buoys ezibekwa ogwini lolwandle lakuleli zijwayele ukulahleka, kodwa isikebhe sokutakula besingakaze sintshontshwe phambilini.
Kucelwa noma ngubani ongaba nolwazi mayelana nokugqekezwa kwendawo ashayele amaphoyisa ase-Strandfontein ku-021 370 1540 noma ashayele i-Crime Stop ku-08600 10111.

JetBlueIndiza yokuqala eyayisuka eNewark, eNew Jersey, yafika eSt. Maarten ngoMgqibelo, Novemba 21st. Abamele iSt. Maarten Tourism Bureau (STB) bebekhona ukwamukela abagibeli kanye nabasebenzi abafika ngamathokheni okubonga.
Kuphinde kwanikezwa noqwembe kubamele iJetBlue egameni likahulumeni nabantu baseSt. Maarten ukukhumbula indiza. Abagibeli abafikayo babingelelwa ngemisindo yomculo we-steelpan futhi banikezwa nogologo we-guavaberry wokunambitha. “Ngijabule kakhulu ukukwazi ukuhamba ngendiza ngisuka eNewark ngiye eSt. Maarten. Kuyangijabulisa ukubuya emuva kwalezi zinyanga ezimbalwa ezedlule, ”kusho uKaputeni weJetBlue uPaul Getman ephawula.
“Sijabule kakhulu ukubona elinye isango iJetBlue livulekele iSt. Maarten neNewark. Lobu bekungubudlelwano obuqhubekayo obusukela ngonyaka ka-2008 ngendiza yethu yokuqala sisuka esikhumulweni sezindiza iJohn F. Kennedy. Njengoba sinamasango amane manje asebenzela iSt. Maarten, kukhombisa ukuzethemba iJetBlue enakho lapho sibheke khona futhi sibheke phambili ekusebenzeni kanzima okuqhubekayo nobudlelwano obuhle bokusebenza esikukhuthazile, ”kusho uMqondisi we-STB uMay-Ling Chun.

KULENDODA edideke ingqondo lakhathesi kulandela ukuthola ukuba ibithandana lenye indoda, nanko besebehlale bonke inyanga ezimbili, isithi ngowesifazana.
Lokhu akula loyedwa ofuna ukuhlangana lakho empilweni kodwa kwenzakele kuJames Mapawa (40) ongumthengisi wempahla odumileyo eNarrans Building enzikini yedolobha le-Kwekwe.
Kubikwa uthole ukuthi isithandwa sakhe uPraise Mpofu (25) akade esehlale laye uyindoda.
Lolu daba luvele ngesikhathi uMapawa exabana loPraise besemacansini. Kubikwa ngoNtulikazi ngosuku olungaziwayo endaweni yobumnandi eKwekwe, uMapawa wahlangana loPraise owayegqoke ezenza umuntu wesifazane.
UMapawa wakhombisa uPraise, bavumelana njalo wamhambisa endlini lapho abaqala ukuhlala khona ndawonye.
Kubikwa mhlaka 7 Mpandula, laba bobabili benza ucansi, ngaleso sikhathi kwavela ukuba uPraise ngowesilisa.
Lokhu kwethusa uMapawa, kwavuka umsindo phakathi kwabo bangqikilana ngezibhakela.
Ngenxa yokucasuka, uMapawa wabikela amapholisa ngodaba, okwadala ukuthi babotshwe bobabili.
Bamiswe phambili kukamantshi weKwekwe u-Itai Kagwere ngecala lokubhinya.
Ababuzwanga ukuthi bayalivuma yini icala kodwa babhadaliswe ibheyili ye-$100 000 umuntu ngamunye.

Futhi iqiniso ukuthi, noma ngabe sinesiphephetha-moya noma iyunithi yokupholisa umoya, njengoba umzimba wakhe umbozwe izinwele - ngaphandle uma kungumjaho ongenazinwele, kunjalo- kungashisa kakhulu.
Ngalesi sizathu, kubaluleke kakhulu ukwazi indlela yokunakekela ikati ehlobo, ikakhulukazi ukugwema ukushaywa ukushisa nokoma, izinkinga ezimbili ezivame kakhulu kule nkathi.
Qiniseka ukuthi
... 
a umtheli wohlobo lomthombo, esizokuthola ukuthengiswa ezitolo zezilwane ezifuywayo neziku-inthanethi.
Mnike ukudla okumanzi
Ikati ehlobo alivamisile ukuphuza kakhulu, okuyinkinga ngoba ngokushisa okukhona, kuyinto ejwayelekile ukulahlekelwa uketshezi (umjuluko). Yize kuliqiniso ukuthi lobu boya bujuluka kuphela ngamapayipi, kusabaluleke kakhulu ukuqinisekisa ukuthi uhlala unamanzi. Ngakho-ke, ngaphezu kokuthi ophuzayo utholakala mahhala, esizokwenza ukuthi mnike amathini okudla okumanzi okungen
...
ushiswa yilanga. Noma ngingaphumi ngaphandle Ngincoma ukuthi kugcinwe leyo ndawo yendlu lapho ukukhanya okuqondile kungena khona ukubeka ithawula lapho ngokwesibonelo ukuze ukwazi ukulala phansi. Ngakolunye uhlangothi, uma kwenzeka ukuthi sinensimu futhi lowo onoboya ethokozela ukuba lapho ehlobo, kufanele sibeke isambulela - asikhohlisi- ekhoneni elithile, noma sitshale izitshalo ezinde ezinikeza umthunzi.

Umhlangano omkhulu weZimbabwe Diaspora Forum obukhangelelwe ngabanengi uqalile ngolwesihlanu eJohannesburg abantu befika kancane-kancane bevela emazweni atshiyeneyo.
Ekhuluma leStudio 7 Umgcinisihlalo wenhlanganiso yeZimbabwe Diaspora Civic Society Organisations Forum uMnumnzana Daniel Molokele uthe ujabule kakhulu ukubona amaZimbabwe aphandle kwelizwe ebuthana ekwakheni iZimbabwe entsha. Uthe okuthokozisayo yikuthi lumhlangano uze waphumelela kungakhathalekile lenhlupho zemali abahlangene lazo kumalungiselelo.
Esinye isikhulumi kulo umhlangano uNkosikazi Violet Mariyacha utshele istudio 7 ukuthi amazwe wonke alezizalwane zeZimbabwe kufanele aziphe imvumo yokuphephela ukuze zisebenze bese zithuthukisa umnotho welizwe lazo. Usole kakhulu amazwe afana leBritain ngokwala ukwemukela labo abadinga ukuphephela.
UMthandazo Dube oze kulo umhlangano emele abaculi labanye abenza imisebenzi yamasiko lenhlalo kazulu, yena uthi ukumanyana yikho kuphela okuzaletha inguquko ezimbabwe. Uthe kulo umhlangano bazakhuthaza ukuthi abamabandla aphikisayo babanjwe ngamandla ukuvezela uzulu amacebo abalawo okuvuselela umnotho weZimbabwe.
Umhlangano lo ongenwa ngamanxusa avela enhlanganisweni ezibalisa eye Zimbabwe Diaspora Civic Organisations Forum, Zimbabwe Diaspora Development Chamber leye Global Zimbabwe, ukhangelelwe ukuqhubekela phambili ngoMqgibelo lapho ingxoxo zizagxila kwezamabhizimusi lomnotho welizwe.

Noma ngabe ufuna ukuhlanza amafasitela wendlu yakho noma ukuvula insiza yokuhlanza amawindi, kubalulekile ukwazi imikhiqizo nemishini ebalulekile oyodinga ukwenza amafasitela akhanye futhi acwebezele. Ukuhlanzwa kwamawindi akuyona into elula ngoba amawindi avezwa uthuli nokungcola usuku lonke. Kodwa-ke, kufanele ubambe ukuthi amafasitela angcolile enza ind
... 
 kakhulu egijima ubude bewindi futhi idlule kulokho okudinga ukususwa.
Uma insingo ilele-ewindini, ngeke uyihlikihle ingilazi. Ukusebenzisa i-window scraper kubalulekile emiphumeleni yobungcweti ngoba ukungcola okukulo ingilazi kuzokukhathaza ngokudala izintambo nenjoloba ye-squeegee.
Ibhakede
Kungazwakala kusobala, kepha udinga ibhakede lesisombululo sakho sokuhlanza amawindi. Kufanele futhi uqiniseke ukuthi unebhakede elanele ngokwanele iwashi lakho. Uma une-washer engu-50 cm kodwa unebhakede 
...
manzi angenakho ukungcola noma ukungcola kuwo) agijimela eshibhini elincane phezulu lapho ibhulashi likhona. Wokuhlanza uzosebenzisa ibhulashi ukuvusa ukungcola engilazini, bese umane ugeza ingilazi.
Le ndlela izoshiya iwindi libukeka limangalisa. Ngeke kube khona noma yimiphi imichilo noma amamaki we-squeegee asele ngemuva. Amafreyimu amawindi abukeka emuhle nawo! Lolu hlobo lokuhlanza amawindi ludinga ikhono elincane, futhi abantu abaningi bangaluthola ngokushesha.

Ukulungiselela ukuhamba kwezikhulu ze-Woza eNanda urban trail, ikhampeyini yokuhlanza yahlelwa ngezi-15 kuLwezi ku-2014. IDurban Green Corridor (DGC) ihlangene ne-Arise & Shine ne Junior Classic F.C. ingxenye yendawo yonke ye-Trial phakathi ko-Ohlange ne Phoenix Settlement yatholwa yilo mphakathi, uqhutshwa ukuhlanzeka. IJunior Classic F.C yayimelwe ngabadlali aba-22 nokhoshi aba-2, uZamokuhle Mnqayi noThubelihle Mnqayi. I-Arise & Shine yayimelwe uFaniza Mbambo, uSfiso Dlamini noLuyanda Mpisi neDGC eyayimelwe uViwe Nkungu, Mlungisi Mthembu noSanele Mvuyane. Izingane zazinikwa amagilavu avikelayo enani eli-70 lezikhwama zikatoti, eziningi ezigcwala ngamahora ambalwa.

Ye. OFakazi bakaJehova bayawenza umsebenzi wobunali loba ngaphi lapho abahlala khona njalo bakukhuthalele ukutshela abantu lokho abakukholwayo.—UMathewu 28:19, 20.
Abanye oFakazi bayahamba bayetshumayela kumbe bayehlala ezindaweni eziselizweni lakibo ezilabantu abanengi abangakezwa izindaba ezinhle eziseBhayibhilini. Ikanti abanye bathuthela kwamanye amazwe ukuze bayetshela abantu abanengi izindaba ezinhle. Bayathokoza ukuba lengxenye ekugcwaliseni isiphrofetho sikaJesu esithi: “Lizakuba ngofakazi bami . . . lasemikhawulweni yomhlaba.”—ImiSebenzi 1:8.
Ngo-1943, savula isikolo ukuze abanye abanali bethu baqeqetshwe kuso. Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, kulaboFakazi abadlula 8 000 asebengene isikolo lesi esaziwa ngokuthi yiSikolo seGiliyadi (Watchtower Bible School of Gilead).

Uhulumende ubikwa esithi uphakathi kwemizamo yokulungisa inhlelo zakhe zemali ngokukhulumisana labosomabhizimusi labanye abaphatheke kuloludaba, ngoba isisindo semali yeZimbabwe siphansi nxa siqathaniswa leyakwamanye amazwe, okuyikho okuvimba ukuthuthuka komnotho welizwe.
Isiphathamandla sikahulumende uNkosikazi Sekai Zenza ubikwa esithi udaba lwemali yilo olubangela ukuthi ilizwe lehluleke ukuzikhandela impahla zalo, lithenngiselane lamanye amazwe, kanye lokufeza uhlelo lokuthi eleZimbabwe libe selinothile ngomnyaka ka 2030.
Uthi ukusebenzisa idola leMelika, lona elisilelayo, yikho okuwisa umnotho welizwe.
Sixoxa lengcwethi ezitshiyeneyo ngendlela yokucubungula loludaba.

Sihlangana loSolakele evukela eFredi ngelanga langoLwesithathu, okwathi nje ilanga lisithi chatsha wayesevele esephundle amazolo, esekude, engoyathenga impahla ezithile.
Wayevunule okwenina njalo ehloniphile njengenkosikazi yomuntu okokuthi lombonayo wayembheka ngelihloniphayo. Wathenga-ke akuthengayo uSolakele wabambisana indlela labakoNdlela baze behlukana entabeni zeMhlolweni.
UPhawundi kusobala ukuthi wayesembonile uSolakele ezitolo, kwathi-ke ngemva kokuthenga kwakhe igwayi wasuka ngesimnyama esiya enkosini yabo enguMlahlwa.
Ngesikhathi uPhawundi efika kuMlahlwa, wamthola evele amehlo esebomvu gebhu esevuke isilo seganga.
Okungathi kwathoba inhliziyo yeganyana leli yikuzwa ukuthi uSolakele wayesemavinkilini njalo kazange ananzelele ukuthi uPhawundi lo wayesembonile.
Wayengasadingi lokuzwa izinto ezinengi wayesejahile okwamagama uMlahlwa, ebonga njalo kuPhawundi ngokumphathela indaba ezinhle kangaka evele wayedinga uSolakele ngamehlo abomvu agebhu.
Latshelela iganyana elinguMlahlwa selivele linukelwa yinyama emakhaleni. Lacandama iganyana, lathula zwi lamelela ukudlula kukaSolakele endleleni.
USolakele wayesebona nje ukuthi ekhaya kwasekuseduze, wezwa efikelwa liculo lokubonga, edumisa iNkosi, duku duku nje engakayiqedi lengoma yakhe iganyana labe selimeqele.

Inhlanganiso yeMedia Monitoring Project of Zimbabwe (MMPZ) isisole kakhulu amaphephandaba kahulumende lomsakazo weZBC ngokwehlisa ubuhlonzi bokuthapha izindaba ngokuthatha uhlangothi kudaba lokulwisana kubandla leZanu PF.
IMMPZ ithi amaphephandaba agoqela eleHerald, leSunday Mail ethula izindaba ezithuka umsekeli kaMongameli Robert Mugabe, uNkosikazi Joice Mujuru njalo akamuphi ithuba lokukhuluma icele lakhe.
Inhlanganiso le ithi amaphephandaba azimeleyo afana leDaily News leNewsDay yiwo ethula indaba ezilohlonzi njalo ezingathathi hlangothi ngokulwisana kuZanu PF.
UNtungamili Nkomo oweStudio Seven uxhume isiphathamandla seMedia Monitoring Project of Zimbabwe, uNkosazana Sibusisiwe Dube ochasisa kabanzi ngalolu daba.

I-PVC Compounds for Compact and Foamed Shoes Soles Production
I-PVC, i-Polyvinyl Chloride iyi-polymer ye-thermoplastic esetshenziswa kakhulu kumjovo wezinyawo zezicathulo.I-PVC Soles yenziwa ikakhulukazi ngenqubo yomjovo oqondile kodwa futhi ingenziwa njengamabhodi egwebu amancane e-PVC afakwe ikhalenda futhi asikwe.Inokumelana okuhle nokuguquguquka kanye nokuhuzuka ngezindleko ezikhangayo.Amasoli e-PVC nawo anezindawo ezinhle zokugquma nokumelana.Abiza kahle futhi aphinde abe enye yesikhumba.
Ngokuhlangenwe nakho kokutadisha nokukhiqiza embonini yezinto ze-PVC iminyaka engaphezu kwengu-28, i-INPVC ibilokhu idumileI-PVC Sole CompoundsAbahlinzeki kanye Nabathekelisa, sinikeza usayizi ofanayo wezinhlayiya eziqinisekisa ukusebenza okuzinzile nokugqamile.
Okwethu okunikezwayoI-PVC Sole Compoundsasetshenziswa kakhulu ekukhiqizeni ama-Shoe Insoles & Outsoles, ama-Slippers, ama-Beach Sandals, amabhuzu, ama-Kids Soles, njll. futhi angenziwa kalula ngezifiso ngokwesidingo sohlelo lwakho lokusebenza.Ungathola le Polyvinyl Chloride Sole Compound kalula ngamamaki ahlukene.
Sinezinhlobo ezilandelayo Zenhlanganisela Yomjovo Wezinyawo Zezinyawo:
* Izinhlamvu ze-PVC zokubumba umjovo wama-insoles ahlangene nama-outsoles
* Izinhlamvu ze-PVC zokubumba umjovo we-foamedama-insoles nama-outsoles
* Izinhlamvu ze-PVC zokubumba umjovo "wokuminyana okuphansi kakhulu" anegwebuama-insoles nama-outsoles(okuhlukile kune-PU foamed soles)

Mogadishu - Kuthunjwe abasebenzi ababili abanikela ngosizo baseKenya nodokotela waseSomalia enyakatho neSomalia, nokusolwa izigebengu zasolwandle, kusho amaphoyisa.
Lokhu kuthunjwa kwenzeke ngaseGalkayo,.
"Kuthunjwe abasebenzi ababili baseKenya nodokotela waseSomalia, kusaphenywa ngalolu daba," kusho isikhulu samaphoyisa aseGalkayo, u-Adan Warsame etshela i-AFP.
Elinye iphoyisa laseGalkayo, uMohammed Ise Hassan, uthe lokhu kuthunjwa kwenzeke ngoLwesithathu ntambama ngaseBaadweyn.

anele futhi zenzeke uma unikeza imininingwane eyengeziwe futhi ulinde. Kufanele futhi ubheke ama-insurers ku-intanethi futhi uthole izingcaphuno ezisheshayo kusuka kuwebhusayithi yazo. Modimolle - Ungqondongqondo ecaleni lokudlwengulwa nokubulawa kwenkosikazi uJohan Kotze, kuzofanele ahambe ayohlolwa ngudokotela wengqondo, kunquma iMansthi eNkantolo yaseModimolle.
"Ngokomthetho wezinkantolo uKotze kumele ahanjiswe esibhedlela sabagula ngekhanda iWeskoppies Psychiatric Hospital aye kohlolwa ngodokotela," kusho iMantshi uHannes
Stoffberg.
"Kumele kuthathwe izinyathelo ngokushesha mayelana noKotze. Uzogqunywa esitokisini kuze kuba kubuya imiphumela yodokotela."
UKotze kuthiwa waphoqa abasebenzi bakwakhe engadini ukuthi badlwengule umkakhe ebakhombe ngesibhamu, waphinde wadubula wabulala indodana kankosikazi angayizali.

Uzothobela umthetho uModise
2014-07-08 10:04
Cape Town - USihlalo weNational Council of Provinces uThandi Modisi uthi uzosebenzisana nabazokwenza uphenyo ngokushiywa kwemfuyo inganakiwe epulazini lakhe, kubike iTimeslive ngoLwesibili.
"Ngidumele kakhulu ngokufa kanye nokuhlukumezeka kwemfuyo ngemuva kokuba abasebenzi behambe bayishiya yodwa epulazini bengangitshelanga,” kusho uModise esitatimendeni.
"Ukuhlukumezeka ezidlule kukhona izilwane ngeke kwafaniswa nemali engilahlekele.”
UModise ubelokhu ecabanga ukuthi konke kuhamba kahle epulazini lakhe njengoba wayeshiye kukhona nemenenja yepulazi.
UModise uthe wayeqashe nabantu abafanele ukubhekana nomsebenzi wezilwane, abahlanganisa nodokotela bazo.
UModise uthi uthuke kabi ngesikhathi ezwa ngokushiywa kwemfuyo yodwa etshelwa ngabakwa-Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals (SPCA).
Izingulube besezidlana zodwa, kanti kubikwa nokuthi beziphuza umchamo wazo. Iziklabhu, yizimbuzi kanye namadada nakho kufele khona epulazini.
I-Freedom Front Plus ngoMsombuluko ithe uModise iyisibonele esimbi kubalimi abamnyama abasafufusa futhi kumele abhekane nengalo yomthetho ngesihluku asikhombise ezilwaneni.
"Ukuba nepulazi kudinga ukuba umuntu asebenze kanzima, akwazi ukunaka ipulazi lakhe, ungabeki umsebenzi kwabanye abantu,” kusho uPieter Groenewald we-FF-Plus.

Akukholakali ukuthi kulo hulumeni obusayo kungaba khona lesi simo. Sihlale sikhuthaza abantu ukuba benze izifundo zobunjiniyela kepha uma sebekhona abasetshenziswa ngendlela engabenza bazizwe njengonjiniyela.
UMnuz Willies Mchunu esengungqongqoshe wathi makubhalwe incwadi, abantu baqashwe ngokugcwele kepha kwangenzeka lokho. Kwafika uMnuz Mxolisi Kaunda njengongqongqoshe naye wathembisa - kodwa kwangaba nashintsho.
Manje sekukhona uMnuz Bheki Ntuli kanti sekuvele kwaba nzima kakhulu njengoba sekusayinwa izinkontileka zezinyanga ezintathu.
Uma ubheka yinto yamabomu le, kukhona abadlayo ngosizi lwalezi zingane. Kodwa elami lithi qaphelani amathenda hulumeni anganiqhathi nabantu abanivotele.
Inkosi impela ngiyafisa ukwazi isizathu esenza abafowethu baphathwe ngalolu hlobo, bayaguga manje, bazele, abanye sebedlulile emhlabeni izingane zisele dengwane akukho lutho olusele ngaphandle nje komlando othi ubaba wayesebenza eMnyangweni wezokuThutha.
Ngithi khuza Khuzeni (Ndunankulu Sihle Zikalala) izwe liyabona.

a.”

Uthi iCosmos ivulele iHungry Lions abebedlala nayo kwiGladAfrica Championship icala lokudlalisa umdlali obengabhalisiwe ngendlela efanele.
Kuvela ukuthi lo mdlali, uTshepo Mohlala wasuka kwiCosmos waya enkulisa yeKaizer Chiefs ngaphambi kokudlulela kwiLions.
Konke lokhu kwenzeka nje iCosmos ayimnikanga incwadi emkhululayo ukuba ajoyine elinye
... 
ucwe amaphuzu lingadliwa yizembe, kusinde ezikaMjomane.
“Sengingakuqinisekisa ukuthi kuthe izolo ngabeka iHungry Lions icala lokungaziphathi kahle kulandela isikhalazo esifakwe yiJomo Cosmos,” kusho uMajavu ngoLwesine ntambama.
“Lezi zinsolo ezibekwe yiJomo Cosmos zithi kunomdlali ogama lakhe nguTshepo Mohlala odlale kungafanele okwenza kube yicala ukudlaliswa kwakhe.
“Njengoba lezi zinsolo ziqhamuke ziyisikhalazo, ngokomthetho yePSL kuzoba yiqembu elifake isikhalazo elizoshushisa leli cala okuy
...
aka ohlwini lwamacala azoqulwa.
“Leli cala selibekelwe ukuba liqulwe ngoJuni 27 (ngoMsombuluko) emahhovisi ePSL. Uma seliwuliwe futhi nesigungu sesiphumile nesinqumo, ngiyobuya ngazise abantu ngalokho.
“Ngikakuqinisekisa nokuthi ukwenzela ukuthi kungabi nakwenzelela futhi konke kwenzeke ngendlela efanele, ngiwazisile wonke amaqembu athintekayo kuleli cala.
“Lokhu ngikwenzele ukuthi uma kukhona elifisa ukuzibandakanya ekuqulweni kwalo likwazi ukuba khona ngisuku lokuqulwa kwalo,” kuchaza uMajavu.

UMengameli wase-Iran u-Ebrahim Raisi ushonile engozini yendiza enophephela emhlane, ngoksho kukahulumeni wase-Iran. Uphinde waqinisekisa ukuthi noNgqongqoshe wezangaPhandle uHossein Amir-Abdollahian kanye nabanye abayisikhombisa nabo bashone kulokhu kuphahlazeka.
Ukushona kukaRaisi kuza ngesikhathi esinzima e-Middle East, njengoba kuqubuka impi e-Gaza. Indiza enophephela emhlane ephahlazeke emasontweni ambalwa i-Iran iqale ukuhlasela kwa-Israyeli nge-drone-and-missile iziphendulela ngemuva kokuh
... 
indlela eziningi ekhuluma kusukela kuqale impi yase-Gaza ngoMfumfu egxeka ukubulawa kwabantu okwenziwe u-Israyeli ngokumelene nama-Palestina, futhi wacela umphakathi wamazwe ngamazwe ukuba ungenelele.
Uthembise ukuziphindiselela kwa-Israyeli ngemuva kokudiliza isakhiwo senxusa lase-Tehran e-Syria futhi kwashona amalungu ayisikhombisa e-Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC), okuhlanganisa nama-generals amabili.
URaisi wamukele ukuziphendulela kwe-Iran ngama-drones nama-missiles kwa-Israel, ini
...
okuzila futhi nefulegi layo lizondizela phansi kulandela ukushona kukaMengameli.
Kulindeleke ukuthi izwe libambe ukhetho ezinsukwini ezingamashumi amahlanu kulandela ukushona kukaMengameli walo okungalindelekile.

Yiziphi izimbangela ezingenzeka zokushaya kwenhliziyo okuphansi?
Uma sikhuluma ngempilo, izinga lokushaya kwenhliziyo ngokuvamile liyinkomba engenakunakwa.Izinga lokushaya kwenhliziyo, inani lezikhathi inhliziyo eshaya ngalo ngomzuzu, ngokuvamile libonisa impilo yemizimba yethu.Nokho, lapho izinga lokushaya kwenhliziyo liwela ngaphansi kwesilinganiso esivamile, kungase kusho ukuthi kukhona okungahambi kahle emzimbeni.Namuhla, sizoxoxa ngezimbangela ezingase zenzeke zokushaya kwenhliziyo ephansi 
... 
nitha yokushaya kwenhliziyo.Lawa madivayisi angarekhoda umsebenzi kagesi wenhliziyo ngesikhathi sangempela futhi asisize siqonde izinguquko ekushayeni kwenhliziyo.Ngesikhathi esifanayo, bangaphinde banikeze ulwazi olubalulekile mayelana nesigqi senhliziyo nesakhiwo senhliziyo, okusisiza ukuthi sithole izinkinga zenhliziyo ngesikhathi.
Ngaphezu kokushaya kwenhliziyo, umfutho wegazi uphinde uyinkomba ebalulekile yempilo yenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi.I-sphygmomanometer iyithuluzi elivamile lokulinga
...
hini yezokwelapha echwepheshile ukuqapha izinkomba zezempilo ezifana nokushaya kwenhliziyo nomfutho wegazi, singasiqonda kangcono isimo sethu somzimba futhi sithole izinkinga zempilo ezingaba khona ngesikhathi.Ngesikhathi esifanayo, kumelwe futhi silondoloze indlela yokuphila enempilo, njengokudla okunempilo nokuvivinya umzimba okusesilinganisweni, ukuze silondoloze impilo yenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi.Masisebenze ngokubambisana ukuvikela impilo ngobuchwepheshe!

THANDOLUHLE NGUBO
INCOME isenzo sikaMnu uJacob Zuma ngesikhathi esangumengameli waseNingizimu Afrika inhloko yamajaji ephumayo kulesi sikhundla, uMnu Raymond Zondo (osesithombeni), yathi wayebonisana nabo bengabaholi bamajaji ngaphambi kokuthatha isinqumo sokunciphisa noma ukukhuphula isabelomali sabo. UZondo ubekhuluma izolo ngoLwesihlanu ngesikhathi ephendula imibuzo yabezindaba ngemuva kokwethula kwakhe umbiko weJudiciary Annual Budget.
Uthe ubuholi bukaMengameli uCyril Ramaphosa buhlulekile wukubonisana nabo ngesikhathi buthatha lesi sinqumo.
“Ngesikhathi sikaZuma, kwabizwa umhlangano wazo zonke izinhloko ezithintekayo, saziswa kusenesikhathi ukuthi isabelomali siyancishiswa. Ekuncishisweni kwesakamuva, sibone sekwenzeka nje, okuyinto engafanele ngoba inhloko yamajaji kumele yaziswe bese kuboniswana ngokuthi ukulimala okungaba ekusebenzeni kwezinkantolo nokunye kungamiswa kanjani,” kusho uZondo.
Uthe wambhalela incwadi umengameli ecela umhlangano wokuchazeleka ngalesi sinqumo, kodwa kwabuya impendulo ethi isinqumo wasithatha (umengameli) ngemuva kokubonisana nongqongqoshe wezemali.
“Kubalulekile ukuthi izakhamizi zakuleli zazi ukuthi kwesinye isikhathi uma singasebenzi ngendlela efanele, yingoba izinto zisuke zingaphezu kwamandla ethu. Sisebenza ngaphansi kwezimo ezinzima ngoba ezinye zezinqumo zithathwa singazi,” esho.

Ugwadule lwaseTabernas lisesifundazweni sase I-Almería. Ngokukhethekile, ihlanganisa indawo engamakhilomitha-skwele angamakhulu amathathu komasipala base USanta Cruz de Marchena, IGador, IGergal, Alboloduy nezakhe Amathaveni.
Kubhekwa njengokuwukuphela kogwadule ku- Europa, ngoba ezinye ezivela eZwekazini Elidala zihlukaniswa njengezindawo eziwugwadule kuphela. Ukuguqulwa kwenhlabathi yawo nesimo sezulu sendawo, nge cishe ukungabi khona kwemvula ngokuphelele, kukhulise indawo eyomile efana ncama
... 
dawo.
ITabernas, idolobha elinika igama lalo ugwadule
Futhi idolobha elinikeza igama lalo ogwadule lwaseTabernas kukufanele ukuvakashelwa ngoba likunikeza okuhehayo okuningi. Leli dolobha lasendulo lamaSulumane lingenye yezindawo ezome kakhulu eYurophu. Ubufakazi obuhle balokhu ukuthi Ipulatifomu ye-Almería Solar, esinye sezikhungo zocwaningo ezinkulu kakhulu ngalolu hlobo lwamandla emhlabeni.
Kepha kuzothakazelisa kakhulu ukubona okwakhe ISonto Lethu Lady of the Incarnation, eyakhiwe ngekhulu l
...
e i-gurullos. Futhi, ngophudingi, ungazama i- ingulube igaya ikhekhe, the Isinkwa seCalatrava noma i ukunitha ama-donuts. Ngokuqondene nesiphuzo, i mampela.
Sengiphetha, njengoba ubona, ugwadule lwamatabernakele kunokuningi angakunika kona. Phakathi kokuhehayo kwayo kunendalo eyingqayizivele, amadolobha amahle anezikhumbuzo, isimo esivamile se- Intshonalanga yaseMelika kanye ne-gastronomy enhle. Bhuka uhambo lwakho manje futhi wazi le ndawo esifundazweni sase-Almería.

ubunjiniyela bemikhiqizo
Coi Technology igxile ekusesheni okuqhubekayo kwezinto ezintsha ezizosetshenziswa ekukhiqizeni kwayo.
Eminyakeni yamuva, izinto zepulasitiki ziye zathuthuka kakhulu, futhi Coi Technology ifake uchungechunge lwe-C-PVC, i-PVC, i-PP, i-PVDF kanye PTFE ama-valve kuyo standukukhiqizwa kwe-ard.

Coi Technology
amaphrojekthi kanye nokubulawa okukhethekile
Inhloso enkulu yokuqaliswa kwephrojekthi yethu ukwaneliseka kwamakhasimende ethu.
Phakathi nesigaba sokuqala sephrojekthi, abasebenzi bethu bezobuchwepheshe bazohlola uhlobo oluhle kakhulu lwezinto ezibonakalayo, becabangela isilinganiso esihle kakhulu sekhwalithi yamanani, ukuze banikeze ukusekelwa okungcono kakhulu kwe-valve yokuphepha.

Ikomkhulu Kule projekthi, isakhiwo sefektri esisetshenzisiwe siguqulwe saba yindawo esebenzayo efaka indawo yokubukisa, i-catwalk kanye nehhovisi lokuklama. Kuphefumulelwe "ukuluka izindwangu", iphrofayli ekhiphe i-aluminium isetshenziswe njengengxenye eyisisekelo yezindonga. Imisuka eyehlukene yemikhawulo ichaza imisebenzi ehlukene yezikhala. Udonga lwe-faƧade lubukeka njenge-coffer enkulu lapho wonke umuntu ongagunyaziwe angavinjwa. Ngaphakathi kwesakhiwo, izinsimbi ezixinene zisetshenziselwa ukwenza zonke izikhala zingabonakali, ukuze kukhuthazwe ukuxhumana phakathi kwama-franchisees nabaqambi.
Igama lephrojekthi : Weaving Space, Igama labaklami : Lam Wai Ming, Igama leklayenti : PMTD Ltd..
Lo mklamo omuhle ungowokuwina umklomelo wokuqamba emncintiswaneni wokuklama imidwebo. Kufanele nakanjani ubone iphothifoliyo yomklamo wabadwebi abawine umklomelo ukuthola eminye imisebenzi eminingi emisha, ekhangayo, yangempela neyokuqamba yemiklamo.

Omama ababili abendileyo abe Chinhoyi eMashonaland West kubikwa bekhandwe kunsukwana ezedluleyo beloya kulandela ukuwa kwabo kukhomani lokuloya.
Unkosikazi Rosemary Kamanga lo Nkosikazi Esnath Maodza abahlala elokitshini le Shackleton duzane ledolobho le Chinhoyi kubikwa ukuthi bawiswa kukhomani lolu ngomunye wabo uNkosikazi Shylet Muzeza bevela loya endaweni okuthiwa yi Alaska.
Kubikwa ukuthi bawela endlini kaMnu. Ernest Mafunga owokholo lwe lwesipositoli owaphaphama emadabukakusa wabathola benqunu besithi badinga omunye wabo lenyama yabafileyo.
Uzulu wathi gwaqa endlini kamMnu. Mafunga lapho omama laba abavuma khona ukuthi ngabathakathi bezigodo.
Kubikwa ukuthi bahanjiswe emapholiseni acine ebafaka emthethwandaba lapho umantshi uMnu. Fanny Nyakudya othe kumele bayehlolwa emakhanda njengoba bengani baphambene.
Umnu. David Mhabinyana Ngwenya inyanga elodumo uthe kuyenzakala ukuthi omama laba ngabathakathi.

PVC Camera Wire
Ucingo oluhlanganisiwe lwensimbi noma ucingo oluvalwe ngopulasitiki, ucingo lwensimbi oluhlanganiswe ne-PVC (ngemuva kwalokhu olubizwa nge-: PVC wire, PE wire), ucingo oluhlanganisiwe lwenza ukukhethwa komkhiqizo wezinto ezisetshenziswayo zekhwalithi, ngokucubungula okujulile ukwenza ipulasitiki nensimbi yensimbi ihlanganiswe ngci, anti-ukuguga, ukumelana nokugqwala, ukuqhekeka anti njll, impilo yensiza iyabanda futhi ishise ngocingo lwensimbi olushisayo izikhathi eziningana, umkhiqizo ohlukahlukene nombala, kungenziwa ngokuya ngesidingo sekhasimende.
Isetshenziswa kabanzi ekuzalaneni kwezilwane, ezolimo kanye nokuvikelwa kwamahlathi, ezasolwandle, amapaki, uthango lwe-zoo, izinkundla zemidlalo, njll., Ne-anti-corrosion yayo, ukulwa nokuguga, impilo yenkonzo ende kunentambo ejwayelekile.
Izinsimbi Zocingo: Ucingo lwensimbi oluhlanganisiwe, ucingo lwensimbi oluhlanganiswe ne-PVC oluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, oluhlaza okotshani, oluphuzi neminye imibala.

Kunokuphikisana ngokuthi yibaphi abadlali okumele babizwe ngezinkakha eNingizimu Afrika. Umkhuba osukhona owokuthi bonke abadlali abake bazimbandakanya nonobhutshuzwayo babizwa ngezinkakha.
Nokho uButhelezi uyawuhlaba kakhulu lo mkhuba osudume kakhulu ebholeni laseNingizimu Afrika.
“Inkinga iqale uma abezindaba seb
... 
Ningizimu Afrika ushaya igoli elilodwa kwiNdebe yoMhlaba bese ubizwe ngenkakha. Ngebhadi iKaizer Chiefs ayikaze ikhiqize enye inkakha ngemuva kwesizukulwane sikaDoctor Khumalo. Uyena yedwa umdlali engimaziyo okumfanele ukubizwa ngenkakha.
UKhanye ubengekho ngesikhathi iChiefs ibhekene neBloemfontein Celtic emdlalweni wezinkakha eToyota Free State Stadium ngeSonto. Lo mdlalo ububhulela amazolo oweChiefs neYoung Africans yaseTanzania, lapho Amakhosi ebhaxabulwe khona yiYanga ngo 4-0, yaqukula iToy
...
nge ibe nayo enye inkakha. Uyena yedwa inkakha engiyaziyo mina. Ngeke ungitshele ukuthi uJabu Pule (osebizwa ngoMahlangu) noJunior Khanye bayizinkakha,” kuqhuba uButhelezi.
“Baphakathi kwabadlali abahle ababethembisa ukuthi bangagcina beyizinkakha kodwa bamosha yonke into. UJabu ungomunye wabadlali abancane abasezingeni eliphezulu ukugqoka ijezi leChiefs kodwa ngeke umbize ngenkakha.
“Inkakha umuntu owaziphatha kahle ngesikhathi edlala ibhola kodwa eNingizimu Afrika sibiza noma ubani ngenkakha.”

Isimemezelo esimangalisayo sokuqaliswa kabusha kobudlelwano bobunxusa phakathi kweSaudi Arabia ne-Iranngenxa yesivumelwano esenziwa yi-Beijing, sigcizelela intshisekelo yohulumeni bezifunda ekunciphiseni ukungezwani – kanye nokuzimisela kwe-China ukusebenzisa amandla ayo omnotho ukuze ikufeze lokho.
Yize izingqapheli, ikakhulukazi izikhulu zaseMelika, zixwayisa ngokuthi iBeijing ikweletwa kakhulu ngalesi sivumelwano, esethulwe ngoLwesihlanu, ukuxoxisana kungase kubonakale njengocingo lokuvusa iW
... 
hina, uthwetshulwe no-Ali Shamkhani, unobhala woMkhandlu Wezokuphepha Kazwelonke wase-Iran, kanye nomeluleki wezokuphepha kuzwelonke waseSaudi uMusaad bin Mohammed Aiban.
Abanye abahlaziyi bathi isivumelwano asimangazanga njengoba bekungase kubonakale kuqala.
La mazwe womabili ayenawo ukhombise ukuzimisela ukuzibandakanya nediplomacy kusukela ngo-2021, okunesisekelo esiningi sokuqalisa kabusha ubudlelwano obabekwa ezingqungqutheleni ezinhlanu e-Iraq nase-Oman, kusho u-Esfandyar Batmanghelidj, is
...
ubhekana neSaudi Arabia, osekunesikhathi eside isebenzisana nayo ebaluleke kakhulu esifundeni saseGulf kodwa manje isingumdlali ongathembeki kangako emehlweni eWashington. .
“Uhulumeni wase-US unemiqondo emibili” kumaSaudis efuna ozakwethu abasha, kusho u-Alterman kuwebhusayithi yalesi sikhungo. “Ifuna amaSaudis athathe umthwalo owandayo wokuphepha kwawo, kepha ayifuni iSaudi Arabia izimele futhi ibukele phansi amasu okuphepha ase-US.”

Okuqukethwe Ikhasi
Hlola iSan Francisco, Usa
Hlola iSan Francisco idolobha elikhulu eCalifornia, indawo ephakathi neBay Area, eyaziwa kakhulu ngomphakathi wayo okhululayo, indawo enamagquma, ubuciko bokwakha abaseVictoria, ubuhle obumangalisayo, inkungu yasehlobo, nokwehlukahlukana okukhulu kobuzwe nokwamasiko. Lezi ngezinye nje zezici zedolobha elenza iSan Francisco yaba elinye lamadolobha avakashelwa kakhulu emhlabeni.
Izifunda zaseSan Francisco
- Isango Legolide. Omakhelwane bemfashini nabaph
... 
kuluhlaza okugadliwe kwe-Conservatory of Flowers, ubuciko besimanjemanje kanye nobuzwe obugxile ku-De Museum, igumbi elikhulu leTiya laseJapan, isakhiwo esisha seCalifornia Academy of Science eklanywe nguRenzo Piano kanye ne-Strybing Arboretum, iqoqo lezitshalo ezivela kuwo wonke umhlaba opholile. Ukuchaza indawo esekude kakhulu yeNyakatho Ntshonalanga yedolobha yiLincoln Park eRichmond, enikezela ukubukwa okuhle kweMarin Headlands, iGolden Gate Bridge ohlangothini lolwandle, kanye nolwandle iPa
...
omuhle ngokubhema kwezinye izindawo. Ngeke bakuhluphe ngokuma nokubhema ngaphandle kwendawo yokudlela noma ibha.
Amabhasikidi angaqashwa ngokuqhamuka ngasogwini oluseNyakatho lwamanzi (iPier 41 / Fisherman's Wharf / Aquatic Park area) noma eduze naseGolden Gate Park uma kuyiwe eMarin County ngeGolden Bridge Bridge. IStanyan ngaseHaight ekugcineni kwepaki kunezitolo eziningi ezinhle. IGolden Gate Transit isebenza futhi iNorth Bay ukusuka eSan Francisco, futhi inama-bike racks emabhasini amaningi.

Selokhu kwethulwe iWindows 8, iMicrosoft yaqala ukuthatha izinyathelo zokuqala ukunikela ngohlelo lokuvikela amagciwane, iMicrosoft ayiyibizi ngokuthi yize kunjalo, esivikela ngayo ezinsongweni ezingenzeka esizithola kwi-inthanethi nsuku zonke . Ngokufika kweWindows 10, iWindows Defender isivele yagqama ohlelweni lokusebenza futhi izinkampani eziningi zama-antivirus zithi lolu hlelo lokusebenza lwendabuko lungumncintiswano ongafanele kuzo zonke lezi zinkampani. IWindows Defender iyi-antivirus es
... 
apho singakwazi sSebenzisa ubungozi bokuhlaselwa ngobugebengu bokweba imininingwane ebucayi futhi lapho kwenziwa khona ubunikazi bewebhusayithi eyaziwa kakhulu. Kepha futhi kusazisa nge-software enonya, amafayela okungenzeka anama-virus nokuningi. Uma sivakashela njalo amakhasi aqukethe lezi zinhlobo zezingozi, kepha siyazi ukuthi senzani, kungenzeka kakhulu ukuthi sikhathele yilesi sikrini esiluhlaza futhi sifuna ukusenza singasebenzi.
Khubaza iSmartscreen ku Windows 10
Ukwenza kungasebenzi ngo
...
ndla noma khubaza isihlungi se-Smartscreen sezinhlelo zokusebenza.
Phakathi kwazo zonke izinketho elisinikeza zona, sikhetha eyokugcina, leyo ekhombisa ukuthi ungenzi lutho (Yenza kungasebenzi iWindows SmartScreen). Ngale ndlela, ngaso sonke isikhathi lapho sihlangabezana nengozi engaba khona lapho sisebenzisa i-inthanethi, Windows 10 ngeke isibonise noma yimiphi imilayezo yokuxwayisa, ngokuya ngolwazi lwabasebenzisi, ingaba yingozi, kunconywa kuphela ukuthi kungasebenzi uma sazi ukuthi senzani.

Njengoba izinkampani eziningi zitshala imali kubuchwepheshe bamafu, okuwukuphela kwethuluzi elidingekayo ukuze lisebenze ukude ithebhulethi. Kuba lula futhi kube lula kimi ukusebenza ngaphandle kwe-iPad yami. Ngandlela thile, ngicabanga ukuthi izinhlelo zokusebenza ezakhelwe izikrini zokuthinta zisebenziseka kalula kakhulu kunesixhumi esibonakalayo somsebenzisi ezinhlelweni eziningi. Futhi, izindleko zethebhulethi zingaphansi kakhulu kwama-laptops amaningi emakethe futhi zinamabhethri ahlala isikhathi eside kakhulu. Ithebhulethi akuyona eyokufunda nje!
